{"lemma":"خُلْسَةٍ","slug":"خُلْسَةٍ","root":"خ.ل.س","root_slug":"خ-ل-س","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11248","n11254","n11255"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8F%D9%84%D9%92%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"something stolen, booty, plunder","examples":[{"text":"جَادَكَ ٱلْغَيْثُ إِذَا ٱلْغَيْثُ هَمَا – يَا زَمَانَ ٱلْوَصْلِ بِٱلْأَنْدَلُسِ – لَمْ يَكُنْ وَصْلُكَ إِلَّا حُلُمًا – فِي ٱلْكَرَى أَوْ خُلْسَةَ ٱلْمُخْتَلِسِ","english":"the rain would befit you if the rain fell – oh the time of reunion in Andalusia – your reunion wasn't but a dream – in the sleep or a surreptitious passing (= something that passes quickly)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"opportunity, chance","examples":[{"text":"هٰذِهِ خُلْسَةٌ فَٱنْتَهِزْهَا!","english":"This is an opportunity so seize it!"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/xul.sa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11248","headword_ar":"خَلَسَهُ","root":"xls","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, MS,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalosN","text_ar":"خَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xil~iysaY","text_ar":"خِلِّيسَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axtlshu","text_ar":"اختلسهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"txl~shu","text_ar":"تخلّسهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He seized it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carried it off, by force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino yadihi","text_ar":"مِنْ يَدِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his hand:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it at an opportunity, with deceit, guile,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circumvention:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took it hastily and openly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he snatched it at unawares; seized it hastily when its owner was unaware:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotilaAsN","text_ar":"اِخْتِلَاسٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"denotes a quicker action than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalosN","text_ar":"خَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lth, K.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalasahu A_iy~aAhu","text_ar":"خَلَسَهُ اـِيَّاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He seized it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carried it off, from him by force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlasotuhu","text_ar":"خَالَسْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I seized the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snatched it away, from him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 139.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*ahu xil~iysaY","text_ar":"اَخَذَهُ خِلِّيسَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AixotilaAsFA","text_ar":"اِخْتِلَاسًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took it by forcible seizure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalosN","text_ar":"خَلْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also in fighting and prostrating: and you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaEonapF","text_ar":"طَعْنَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Axtls","text_ar":"اختلس","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He seized an opportunity to inflict a thrust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wound, with a spear or the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaruhu","text_ar":"بَصَرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Auxotulisa","text_ar":"اُخْتُلِسَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His sight was suddenly taken away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A * and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mls","text_ar":"ملس"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","MS","Mgh","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n11254","headword_ar":"خَلْسَةٌ","root":"xls","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalasahu","text_ar":"خَلَسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single act of seizing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carrying off, by force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (Msb.)       -A2-  It also occurs in a trad., where, if correctly related, it is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalosapN","text_ar":"خَلْسَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n11255","headword_ar":"خُلْسَةٌ","root":"xls","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalasahu","text_ar":"خَلَسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) [which may perhaps mean that it has the abstract sense of the inf. n.: and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seized,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carried off, by force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taken at an opportunity, with deceit, guile,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"circumvention;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or ]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taken hastily and openly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snatched at unawares:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spoil; plunder; booty; a thing taken by spoliation and force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliysapN","text_ar":"خَلِيسَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which last also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an animal that is snatched from a beast or bird of prey and dies before it has been legally slaughtered;"},{"kind":"text","text":"in consequence of which it is forbidden [to be eaten]. (TA.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA qaToEa fiY Alxulosapi","text_ar":"لَا قَطْعَ فِى الخُلْسَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall be no amputation"},{"kind":"text","text":"(of the right hand)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the case of a thing seized,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carried off, by force;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (Mgh, Msb.) [See also an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hu*ay~aA","text_ar":"حُذَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H*Y","text_ar":"حذى"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An opportunity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*ihi xulosapN faA@notahizohaA","text_ar":"هٰذِهِ خُلْسَةٌ فَا@نْتَهِزْهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is an opportunity, therefore do thou take it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seize it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mixture of whiteness with blackness"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the hair, (S, Ham p. 387, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in equal proportions:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of more blackness than whiteness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a predominance of whiteness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliysN","text_ar":"خَلِيسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mixture of fresh and dry portions"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"green and white"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 4)] in herbage. (S, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}